OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mix of
OL,6,Fcloud and clear spells this evening
OL,7,Fand overnight with the risk of a few
OL,8,Fspots of rain, mainly along the south
OL,9,Fcoast overnight. Rather breezy in
OL,10,Fplaces, particularly near coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FAny remaining outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain clearing the south coast early
OL,14,FSunday. Otherwise a largely dry and
OL,15,Fbright day with sunny spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping. Feeling cooler with a
OL,17,Ffreshening breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
